## ── PART 8: Best Practices ─────────────────────────
##
## Here are best practices for training models:
##
## 1. Start simple, increase complexity if needed
## 2. Split data into train/test
## 3. Monitor both training and test error
## 4. Use early stopping
## 5. Normalize your data
## 6. Clean your data
## 7. Try different numbers of epochs
##
## ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────

print("PART 8: Best Practices")
print("───────────────────────")
print("")

print("Best practices:")
print("  1. Start simple")
print("  2. Split data into train/test")
print("  3. Monitor both errors")
print("  4. Use early stopping")
print("  5. Normalize your data")
print("  6. Clean your data")
print("  7. Try different epoch counts")
print("")

